肖恩·列侬开玩笑说艾玛·斯通应该在《可怜的事情》之后扮演他的父亲约翰https://www.nme.com/news/film/sean-lennon-jokes-emma-stone-should-play-his-dad-john-after-poor-things-3600043?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sean-列侬笑话艾玛斯通应该在可怜的事情之后扮演他的爸爸约翰Emma WilkesTue, 12 Mar 2024 11:23:08 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3600043 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sean-lennon-emma-stone.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="肖恩·列侬和艾玛·斯通" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sean-lennon-emma-stone.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sean-lennon-emma-stone-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sean-lennon-emma-stone-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sean-lennon-emma-stone-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sean-lennon-emma-stone-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sean-lennon-emma-stone-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我认为，如果你想成为一名演员，那么下一个明显的步骤就是真正努力并成为约翰·列侬”</p><p>肖恩·列侬<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sean-lennon-jokes-emma-stone-should-play-his-dad-john-after-poor-things-3600043">(Sean Lennon) 开玩笑说艾玛·斯通 (Emma Stone) 应该在《Poor Things》</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上后扮演他的父亲约翰 (John)。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sean-lennon-emma-stone.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="肖恩·列侬和艾玛·斯通" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sean-lennon-emma-stone.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sean-lennon-emma-stone-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sean-lennon-emma-stone-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sean-lennon-emma-stone-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-